{"tid":400350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[淒涼] 韓國商人無錢交租 因大陸客減少 中文從明洞消失","createTime":"2017-09-14T17:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T00:04:46.000Z","uid":82845,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8d560132c1772b6a0a84f55fa01dc9dd43ac8c","tid":400350,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"明洞街頭冷清<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170914/photo/bknint-20170914103020322-0914_17011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170914%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170914103020322-0914_17011_001_01b.jpg&h=7be88f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明洞是南韓首爾著名商業區，往年每逢中國十一長假，當地商戶總是期待能借大批來韓華客團的龐大購買力「大賺一筆」，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">受薩德風波影響</span>，今年業界已打消了這份期待。有南韓媒體周三（13日）發表題為《中文已從明洞消失》的文章，隨文所附<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圖片可見明洞街頭蕭條冷清，商舖顧客稀少，不少甚至已經倒閉，櫥窗上曾經貼滿以中文攬客的宣傳海報亦已被撤下。</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在明洞經營服裝店15年的金姓老闆表示，現在每天的人流只約有原來的30%，每天進店的中國遊客也就幾個人，<span style=\"color: red;\">店裏原本有10名「導購」，今年已辭退9人</span>。另一名在明洞經營化妝品店的店主稱，目前中國遊客不到原來的一半，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然日本遊客比原來多了一點，但購買力完全不能和華客團相提並論</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n很多曾專門做中國遊客生意的明洞商人紛表無奈，一名女裝店老闆稱，店裏的衣服都是中國人喜歡的款式，導購都會中文，其本人也學了點中文，「但現在要想通過其他辦法克服困難，真的很迷茫」。另有一家飯店老闆也<span style=\"color: red;\">指着對面櫥窗貼滿打折廣告的服裝店說：「他們家原來生意挺好的，但現在估計連房租都交不起了。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n報道更指，大部分明洞商人都認為，這種慘況還會持續下去，尤其最近南韓政府決定臨時追加部署薩德後，他們「復活」的可能性已經蕩然無存。此外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>很多商人認為，不只是中國遊客，連其他國家的遊客也開始遠離明洞</strong></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170914/bknint-20170914103020322-0914_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170914%2Fbknint-20170914103020322-0914_17011_001.html&d=6thh5KiC77SJG6C9dEtp2G6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ab0bdad1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170914/bknint-20170914103020322-0914_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9889dcbc08a22b220b6ebf13b6912427ce58f10","tid":400350,"uid":81037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:26:10.000Z","msg":"上個月去仲係好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過支那人係小左"},{"pid":"65b5f2fe65c88d99bcc03e9a22693cd9d69b1fc2","tid":400350,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:31:39.000Z","msg":"乃共的下場"},{"pid":"f72517d2b86156a222bd9cd06e110f5263902fd5","tid":400350,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78b8268abe8771dbc46a7776ced0eb92f1791df","tid":400350,"uid":23218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"幾時先肯唔黎香港"},{"pid":"97fe0f7fb7f67a0a63201d24684b2e41e13735c1","tid":400350,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b60d59150a1a80d2272bb60a9b6d4f93acde44","tid":400350,"uid":13132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:40:37.000Z","msg":"攬炒啦支那狗泡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9671b5858f07edbe33091d80d39f7aa73c893ee","tid":400350,"uid":17387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:44:44.000Z","msg":"On9 我前兩個月去<br />\n果排成日落雨<br />\n次次去都多人到閪咁 <br />\n周街都係大陸人啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個記者9成搵最少人時間嘅位黎影<br />\n利申：反韓"},{"pid":"40f138ddac1f53b7dea0349a25ebbecbb98469db","tid":400350,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:14:21.000Z","msg":"好淒涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLhvMgucWns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNLhvMgucWns&d=6thh5KiC77SJG6C9dEtp2G6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=01d18342\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLhvMgucWns</a>"},{"pid":"cef72e599f2e93fe99f33f35070bf9ad9b111307","tid":400350,"uid":56287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T22:10:02.000Z","msg":"唔應該賺嘅錢係唔應該畀佢繼續<br />\n就= 香港啲藥房咁"},{"pid":"8b7c907603fa08b9a8abeff599e9e5ce28686c9d","tid":400350,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"幾時先可以發展到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76faa7616fd6f1eacb7e4286ac5a494fa5745a46","tid":400350,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T00:03:38.000Z","msg":"重遊明洞新村可以嗎"},{"pid":"bbc711541b0058dce2496bb819f2da8227dc6c5a","tid":400350,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T00:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}